ivots mid-sentence into song: "The sun revolves around the earth revolves around the sun."  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 0aAmerican poetryy21st century. 7aPOETRY / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of California Press Backlist Package 2000-2013z978311069042240uhttps://doi.org/10.1525/978052094827340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780520948273423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780520948273/original  a978-3-11-069042-2  University of California Press Backlist Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles